sequenceDiagram
    participant PROD as Produtor
    participant PORT as AsyncJobQueuePort
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant ACT as Actor Dramatiq
    participant BR as Bridge
    participant CORE as JobCoreExecutor
    participant PAY as AsyncJobPayloadExecutor
    participant DOM as Handler de domínio
    participant DB as PostgresJobRunStore

    PROD->>PORT: publica QueuedJobEnvelope
    PORT->>MQ: publica payload versionado
    MQ->>ACT: entrega mensagem
    ACT->>ACT: valida schema, version e role
    ACT->>BR: delega payload
    BR->>CORE: execute(envelope)
    CORE->>DB: create_run + append_event
    CORE->>PAY: chama bridge registrado
    PAY->>DOM: executa comando tipado
    DOM-->>PAY: retorna ou falha
    CORE->>DB: transition_status + event terminal
